576
00:51:14,810 --> 00:51:17,810
Living today to the best of my abilities...

577
00:51:18,040 --> 00:51:19,509
as if it were a gift.

578
00:51:21,009 --> 00:51:24,420
That's the best way to repay the kindness...

579
