636
00:58:37,920 --> 00:58:38,920
Yes.

637
00:58:40,150 --> 00:58:41,290
Thank you.

638
00:58:41,520 --> 00:58:42,619
You could have gotten hurt.

639
00:58:42,850 --> 00:58:45,319
